Pet Health Tracker Web Application
Overview
A comprehensive browser-based application for managing pet health records. Store profiles, track medical history, set reminders, and share pet information securely. All data is synchronized with your Google account for secure access across devices.

Features
üêæ Core Features
Pet Profiles:

Save detailed profiles (name, breed, age, weight)

Microchip information tracking

Mood tracking with emoji indicators

Emergency contact storage

Photo uploads with secure cloud storage

Health Management:

Allergy and medical history logs

Custom diet plans

Vaccination/deworming reminders

Medical check-up scheduling

Grooming reminders

